"use strict";(self.webpackChunkmocpilot_docs=self.webpackChunkmocpilot_docs||[]).push([[7506],{9376:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"archive":{"blogPosts":[{"id":"/2026/02/28/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2026/02/28/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-02-28-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.2.3","description":"\ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2026.2.3 \u2014 Vylep\u0161en\xed dashboardu a opravy hub\u016f","date":"2026-02-28T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"}],"readingTime":0.78,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.2.3","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev"]},"unlisted":false,"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.2.2","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2026/02/18/post"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2026.2.3 \u2014 Vylep\u0161en\xed dashboardu a opravy hub\u016f\\n\\nS radost\xed oznamujeme vyd\xe1n\xed **MOCPilot 2026.2.3**, dostupn\xe9 pro **Android**, **iOS** a **macOS**.\\n\\nTato aktualizace zlep\u0161uje pr\xe1ci s dashboardem a opravuje n\u011bkolik d\u016fle\u017eit\xfdch probl\xe9m\u016f s huby a editorem.\\n\\n---\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \u2728 Co je nov\xe9ho v 2026.2.3?\\n\\n### \ud83e\uddf1 Vylep\u0161en\xed dashboardu\\n\\n- Nyn\xed m\u016f\u017eete **duplikovat dashboard controllery**, s volbou **kop\xedrovat v\u0161echny vlastnosti** nebo **kop\xedrovat pouze podle typu**\\n- **P\u0159epracovan\xe1 paleta** pro rychlej\u0161\xed stav\u011bn\xed: zobrazuje se pod dashboardem, m\xe1 tla\u010d\xedtko pro vymaz\xe1n\xed, po p\u0159id\xe1n\xed komponent se nezav\xedr\xe1 a udr\u017euje konzistentn\xed v\xfdb\u011br sekce\\n\\n### \ud83d\udd0c Aktualizace a opravy hub\u016f\\n\\n- **Mould King 4.0** p\u0159eimplementov\xe1n na **nov\xfd protokol na iOS** (Android nad\xe1le pou\u017e\xedv\xe1 p\u0159edchoz\xed protokol)\\n- Opraven probl\xe9m, kdy se **boolean blok \u201ehub je p\u0159ipojen\u201c** nezobrazil, kdy\u017e hub inzeroval (advertising)\\n- Opraven bug, kdy **blok sv\u011btla** mohl p\u0159estat fungovat kv\u016fli zpracov\xe1n\xed p\u0159\xedkaz\u016f start/stop motoru\\n\\n### \ud83d\udee0 Opravy\\n\\n- Opravena validace e-mailu ve vstupn\xed komponent\u011b, kter\xe1 mohla povolit neplatn\xe9 adresy jako `mail@domain.`\\n\\n---\\n\\nAktualizujte na **2026.2.3** pro plynulej\u0161\xed pr\xe1ci s dashboardem a spolehliv\u011bj\u0161\xed chov\xe1n\xed hub\u016f nap\u0159\xed\u010d platformami."},{"id":"/2026/02/18/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2026/02/18/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-02-18-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.2.2","description":"\ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2026.2.2 \u2014 Roz\u0161\xed\u0159en\xe1 podpora hub\u016f a aktualizace ovl\xe1d\xe1n\xed","date":"2026-02-18T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"}],"readingTime":1.05,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.2.2","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.2.3","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2026/02/28/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.1.0","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2026/01/10/post"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2026.2.2 \u2014 Roz\u0161\xed\u0159en\xe1 podpora hub\u016f a aktualizace ovl\xe1d\xe1n\xed\\n\\nS pot\u011b\u0161en\xedm oznamujeme vyd\xe1n\xed **MOCPilot 2026.2.2**, nyn\xed dostupn\xe9ho pro **Android**, **iOS** a **macOS**.\\n\\nTato verze v\xfdrazn\u011b roz\u0161i\u0159uje hardwarovou kompatibilitu a p\u0159in\xe1\u0161\xed nov\xe9 v\xfdkonn\xe9 programovac\xed bloky pro pokro\u010dilou interakci s huby.\\n\\n---\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \u2728 Co je nov\xe9ho ve verzi 2026.2.2?\\n\\n### \ud83c\udd95 Nov\xe1 podpora hub\u016f\\n\\n- **Mould King 4.0 huby** jsou nyn\xed pln\u011b podporov\xe1ny  \\n- **Mould King 6.0 huby** jsou nyn\xed pln\u011b podporov\xe1ny  \\n- **LEGO WeDo 2.0 hub** je nyn\xed pln\u011b podporov\xe1n  \\n\\n---\\n\\n### \ud83d\udd0c Podpora senzor\u016f\\n\\n- WeDo 2.0 senzor n\xe1klonu  \\n- WeDo 2.0 pohybov\xfd senzor \\n\\n---\\n\\n### \ud83e\uddf1 Nov\xe9 programovac\xed bloky\\n\\nTato verze p\u0159in\xe1\u0161\xed nov\xe9 ud\xe1lostn\xed a \u0159\xeddic\xed bloky, kter\xe9 roz\u0161i\u0159uj\xed mo\u017enosti interakce s huby v re\xe1ln\xe9m \u010dase.\\n\\n#### \ud83d\udd04 Ud\xe1lostn\xed bloky senzor\u016f hubu\\n- **Zm\u011bna dat akcelerometru hubu**  \\n- **Zm\u011bna n\xe1klonu hubu**  \\n- **Zm\u011bna orientace hubu**  \\n- **Zm\u011bna \xfarovn\u011b baterie v\u0161ech hub\u016f**\\n\\nTyto bloky umo\u017e\u0148uj\xed va\u0161emu programu okam\u017eit\u011b reagovat na pohyb, rotaci a zm\u011bny nap\xe1jen\xed.\\n\\n#### \ud83d\udd0c \u0158\xeddic\xed bloky p\u0159ipojen\xed hubu\\n- **P\u0159ipojit hub**\\n- **Odpojit hub**\\n\\nNyn\xed m\u016f\u017eete spravovat p\u0159ipojen\xed hub\u016f p\u0159\xedmo b\u011bhem b\u011bhu programu.  \\nTo umo\u017e\u0148uje znovu p\u0159ipojit hub bez restartov\xe1n\xed programu v p\u0159\xedpad\u011b ztr\xe1ty spojen\xed, co\u017e \u010din\xed projekty odoln\u011bj\u0161\xedmi a flexibiln\u011bj\u0161\xedmi.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### \u2699\ufe0f Vylep\u0161en\xed\\n\\n- Zlep\u0161en\xe1 celkov\xe1 stabilita syst\xe9mu  \\n- Optimalizace v\xfdkonu pro plynulej\u0161\xed interakci s huby  \\n- Drobn\xe1 vylep\u0161en\xed u\u017eivatelsk\xe9ho rozhran\xed a rozlo\u017een\xed  \\n\\n---\\n\\nAktualizujte MOCPilot na nejnov\u011bj\u0161\xed verzi a za\u010dn\u011bte tvo\u0159it s roz\u0161\xed\u0159enou kompatibilitou hub\u016f a v\xfdkonn\xfdmi mo\u017enostmi \u0159\xedzen\xed v re\xe1ln\xe9m \u010dase na v\u0161ech sv\xfdch za\u0159\xedzen\xedch."},{"id":"/2026/01/10/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2026/01/10/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-10-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.1.0","description":"\ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2026.1.0 \u2014 Aktualizace funkc\xed a stability","date":"2026-01-10T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"}],"readingTime":1.03,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.1.0","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.2.2","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2026/02/18/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/12/28/post"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2026.1.0 \u2014 Aktualizace funkc\xed a stability\\n\\nS radost\xed oznamujeme vyd\xe1n\xed **MOCPilot 2026.1.0**, nyn\xed dostupn\xe9 pro **Android**, **iOS** a **macOS**.\\n\\nTato verze p\u0159in\xe1\u0161\xed **re\u017eim hosta**, zlep\u0161uje pou\u017eitelnost na mobiln\xedch za\u0159\xedzen\xedch a obsahuje d\u016fle\u017eit\xe9 opravy stability a v\xfdkonu nap\u0159\xed\u010d v\u0161emi platformami.\\n\\n---\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \u2728 Co je nov\xe9ho ve verzi 2026.1.0?\\n\\n### \ud83c\udd95 Novinky\\n- **Re\u017eim hosta** \u2014 pou\u017e\xedvejte aplikaci bez \xfa\u010dtu, s mo\u017enost\xed si ho pozd\u011bji vytvo\u0159it\\n- V\xfdb\u011br jazyka p\u0159id\xe1n na p\u0159ihla\u0161ovac\xed/autoriza\u010dn\xed obrazovku\\n- Aplikace nyn\xed blokuje pou\u017eit\xed hub\u016f s nepodporovan\xfdm firmwarem a zobraz\xed jasn\xe9 varov\xe1n\xed\\n\\n### \u2699\ufe0f Vylep\u0161en\xed\\n- Vylep\u0161en\xe9 p\u0159etahov\xe1n\xed blok\u016f na mobiln\xedch za\u0159\xedzen\xedch (lep\u0161\xed dotykov\xe9 ovl\xe1d\xe1n\xed, m\xe9n\u011b necht\u011bn\xfdch interakc\xed)\\n- Paleta blok\u016f se nyn\xed p\u0159i p\u0159etahov\xe1n\xed na mobilu automaticky skryje\\n- U dialog\u016f s upozorn\u011bn\xedm se nyn\xed aplikuje rozmaz\xe1n\xed pozad\xed\\n- Vylep\u0161en\xe9 zad\xe1v\xe1n\xed textu nap\u0159\xed\u010d v\u0161emi platformami\\n- Plynulej\u0161\xed ovl\xe1d\xe1n\xed hubu se sn\xed\u017eenou latenc\xed\\n\\n### \ud83d\udee0 Opravy\\n- Opraveno v\xedce probl\xe9m\u016f s drag & drop blok\u016f, v\u010detn\u011b zaseknut\xfdch blok\u016f a ztr\xe1ty vstupu my\u0161i/dotyku\\n- Opraveny p\xe1dy p\u0159i zastaven\xed program\u016f pou\u017e\xedvaj\xedc\xedch vlastn\xed (\u201eMoje\u201c) bloky\\n- Opraveno, \u017ee kalibrace \u0159\xedzen\xed (steering rack) se nevracela do st\u0159edu\\n- Opraveno zpo\u017ed\u011bn\xed ovl\xe1d\xe1n\xed hubu a pomal\xe1 odezva motoru\\n- Opraveny probl\xe9my v editoru port\u016f, posuvn\xedc\xedch a bloc\xedch rychlosti\\n- Opraven probl\xe9m s hlavn\xedm dialogem a r\u016fzn\xe9 chyby rozlo\u017een\xed UI\\n- Aktualizovan\xe9 p\u0159eklady a drobn\xe9 vizu\xe1ln\xed opravy\\n\\n---\\n\\nAktualizujte MOCPilot na nejnov\u011bj\u0161\xed verzi a u\u017eijte si plynulej\u0161\xed, stabiln\u011bj\u0161\xed a p\u0159\xedstupn\u011bj\u0161\xed z\xe1\u017eitek na v\u0161ech sv\xfdch za\u0159\xedzen\xedch."},{"id":"/2025/12/28/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/12/28/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-12-28-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4","description":"\ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4 \u2014 Aktualizace stability a u\u017eivatelsk\xe9ho z\xe1\u017eitku","date":"2025-12-28T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"}],"readingTime":0.59,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2026.1.0","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2026/01/10/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.2.0","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/11/15/post"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4 \u2014 Aktualizace stability a u\u017eivatelsk\xe9ho z\xe1\u017eitku\\n\\nS pot\u011b\u0161en\xedm oznamujeme vyd\xe1n\xed **MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4**, nyn\xed dostupn\xe9 pro **Android**, **iOS** a **macOS**.\\n\\nTato verze se zam\u011b\u0159uje na **plynulej\u0161\xed chov\xe1n\xed**, **vy\u0161\u0161\xed spolehlivost** a **vylep\u0161en\xed u\u017eivatelsk\xe9ho rozhran\xed** nap\u0159\xed\u010d v\u0161emi platformami.\\n\\n---\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \u2728 Co je nov\xe9ho ve verz\xedch 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4?\\n\\n- Plynulej\u0161\xed a stabiln\u011bj\u0161\xed chov\xe1n\xed d\xedky vylep\u0161en\xe9 \u010dasov\xe9 logice\\n- Zlep\u0161en\xe1 synchronizace profil\u016f a spolehlivost aktualizac\xed\\n- P\u0159ehledn\u011bj\u0161\xed rozlo\u017een\xed seznamu profil\u016f\\n- Vylep\u0161en\xfd vzhled a interakce aura posuvn\xedku\\n- Opraven\xe9 probl\xe9my s invertovan\xfdm n\xe1klonem a rotac\xed ovl\xe1d\xe1n\xed\\n- Vylep\u0161en\xe9 rozlo\u017een\xed UI na telefonech a tabletech\\n- Opraven\xe9 barevn\xe9 a p\u0159ep\xednac\xed prvky\\n- Lep\u0161\xed p\u0159eklady a konzistence text\u016f\\n- Obecn\xe9 opravy chyb, zlep\u0161en\xed v\xfdkonu a stability\\n\\n---\\n\\nAktualizujte MOCPilot na nejnov\u011bj\u0161\xed verzi a u\u017eijte si plynulej\u0161\xed a spolehliv\u011bj\u0161\xed pr\xe1ci na v\u0161ech za\u0159\xedzen\xedch."},{"id":"/2025/11/15/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/11/15/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-11-15-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.2.0","description":"\ud83d\ude80 P\u0159edstavujeme MOCPilot 2025.2.0 \u2014 Ofici\xe1ln\xed multiplatformn\xed vyd\xe1n\xed!","date":"2025-11-15T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"}],"readingTime":0.54,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.2.0","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/12/28/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.9","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/06/3/post"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 P\u0159edstavujeme MOCPilot 2025.2.0 \u2014 Ofici\xe1ln\xed multiplatformn\xed vyd\xe1n\xed!\\n\\nS pot\u011b\u0161en\xedm oznamujeme ofici\xe1ln\xed vyd\xe1n\xed **MOCPilot 2025.2.0**, nyn\xed dostupn\xe9 na **Androidu**, **iOS** a **macOS**!\\n\\nTato verze p\u0159edstavuje v\xfdznamn\xfd krok vp\u0159ed. Aplikace d\u0159\xedve zn\xe1m\xe1 jako **Controlz** byla p\u0159ejmenov\xe1na na **MOCPilot**.  \\nNov\xfd n\xe1zev l\xe9pe odr\xe1\u017e\xed \xfa\u010del aplikace a jej\xed budouc\xed sm\u011b\u0159ov\xe1n\xed \u2014 b\xfdt jednotn\xfdm \u201epilotem\u201c pro va\u0161e LEGO\xae modely, s pokro\u010dil\xfdm ovl\xe1d\xe1n\xedm, programov\xe1n\xedm a intuitivn\u011bj\u0161\xedm prost\u0159ed\xedm.\\n\\n---\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \u2728 Novinky ve verzi 2025.2.0\\n\\n- Sjednocen\xe9 vyd\xe1n\xed pro Android, iOS a macOS  \\n- Zlep\u0161en\xe1 stabilita, v\xfdkon a odezva u\u017eivatelsk\xe9ho rozhran\xed  \\n- Nov\xe1 identita a zna\u010dka *MOCPilot*  \\n- Pokra\u010duj\xedc\xed podpora LEGO\xae Control+, BuWizz 2/3 a dal\u0161\xedch Bluetooth modul\u016f  \\n\\n---\\n\\nSt\xe1hn\u011bte si MOCPilot na sv\xe9 za\u0159\xedzen\xed a objevte novou \xfarove\u0148 ovl\xe1d\xe1n\xed va\u0161ich LEGO\xae v\xfdtvor\u016f!"},{"id":"/2025/06/3/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/06/3/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-06-3-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.9","description":"\ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.1.9 je nyn\xed dostupn\xfd v Mac App Store!","date":"2025-06-03T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.3,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.9","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.2.0","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/11/15/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.5","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/05/17/post"}},"content":"import { MacAppStoreBadge } from \'@site/src/pages/\';\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.1.9 je nyn\xed dostupn\xfd v Mac App Store!\\n\\nS pot\u011b\u0161en\xedm oznamujeme vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.9 jako nativn\xed aplikace pro macOS!\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\nNyn\xed si m\u016f\u017eete u\u017e\xedvat pln\xfd v\xfdkon na plo\u0161e a bezprobl\xe9movou integraci s macOS.  \\nSt\xe1hn\u011bte si ji je\u0161t\u011b dnes z Mac App Store a z\xedskejte kontrolu nad sv\xfdmi LEGO\xae v\xfdtvory jako nikdy p\u0159edt\xedm!\\n\\n<MacAppStoreBadge/>"},{"id":"/2025/05/17/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/05/17/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-05-17-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.5","description":"Popis","date":"2025-05-17T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.46,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.5","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.9","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/06/3/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.4","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/05/10/post"}},"content":"### Popis\\n\\nTato aktualizace zlep\u0161uje pr\xe1ci s bloky, zvy\u0161uje v\xfdkon a zaji\u0161\u0165uje spr\xe1vnou funk\u010dnost na nov\u011bj\u0161\xedch verz\xedch Androidu.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Zm\u011bny\\n\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba p\u0159i skenov\xe1n\xed hub\u016f na Androidu 12+** \u2013 nyn\xed se vy\u017eaduje opr\xe1vn\u011bn\xed k p\u0159esn\xe9 poloze.\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1na mo\u017enost skr\xfdt/zobrazit paletu blok\u016f** kliknut\xedm na pr\xe1v\u011b vybranou kolekci blok\u016f.\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1na rukoje\u0165 pro zm\u011bnu velikosti** palety blok\u016f pro **ru\u010dn\xed \xfapravu velikosti**.\\n- **Opraven\xe9 vysok\xe9 zat\xed\u017een\xed CPU**, kdy\u017e byl profil na\u010dten, ale program nebyl spu\u0161t\u011bn.\\n- **Vylep\u0161en\xfd editor bloku \u201eSeznam \u0159et\u011bzc\u016f\u201c**, aby se zabr\xe1nilo o\u0159ez\xe1v\xe1n\xed obsahu. Polo\u017eky jsou nyn\xed rozd\u011bleny do sloupc\u016f pro lep\u0161\xed p\u0159ehlednost u dlouh\xfdch seznam\u016f."},{"id":"/2025/05/10/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/05/10/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-05-10-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.4","description":"Popis","date":"2025-05-10T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.77,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.4","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.5","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/05/17/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.2 \u2013 2025.1.3","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/04/19/post"}},"content":"### Popis\\n\\nTato aktualizace zlep\u0161uje podporu pro tablety, p\u0159id\xe1v\xe1 u\u017eite\u010dn\xe9 testovac\xed str\xe1nky a opravuje n\u011bkolik probl\xe9m\u016f s kompatibilitou a v\xfdkonem.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Zm\u011bny\\n\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1no rozvr\u017een\xed pro tablety** pro lep\u0161\xed vyu\u017eit\xed v\u011bt\u0161\xedch obrazovek.\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba, kdy se blok \u201etla\u010d\xedtko na hubu stisknuto\u201c** zobrazoval i pro huby, kter\xe9 tuto akci nepodporuj\xed. Tak\xe9 opraveny **bloky pro barevn\xfd senzor** u nepodporovan\xfdch hub\u016f (nap\u0159. BuWizz).\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba, kdy blok \u201eb\u011bh motoru\u201c** neovliv\u0148oval motory bez enkod\xe9r\u016f kv\u016fli chyb\u011bj\xedc\xedm alternativn\xedm p\u0159\xedkaz\u016fm.\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1na str\xe1nka pro testov\xe1n\xed tla\u010d\xedtek gamepadu.**\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1na str\xe1nka pro testov\xe1n\xed hubu** s p\u0159ehledem informac\xed, p\u0159ipojen\xfdch za\u0159\xedzen\xed na portech a stavem ot\u0159es\u016f port\u016f.\\n- **Opraven\xfd nespr\xe1vn\xfd v\xfdklad dat z akcelerometru** pro BuWizz 2 a 3, kter\xfd zp\u016fsoboval chybn\xe9 orienta\u010dn\xed \xfadaje.\\n- **Opraven\xe9 \xfaniky pam\u011bti RAM**, kter\xe9 vedly k ukon\u010den\xed aplikace na n\u011bkter\xfdch za\u0159\xedzen\xedch kv\u016fli vysok\xe9 spot\u0159eb\u011b pam\u011bti.\\n- **Opraven\xe9 chyby p\u0159i na\u010d\xedt\xe1n\xed profil\u016f**, kter\xe9 d\u0159\xedve zp\u016fsobovaly p\xe1dy aplikace v ur\u010dit\xfdch sc\xe9n\xe1\u0159\xedch.\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba na Androidu**, kdy uvoln\u011bn\xed p\xe1\u010dek gamepadu nenastavilo hodnoty os zp\u011bt na nulu."},{"id":"/2025/04/19/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/04/19/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-04-19-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.2 \u2013 2025.1.3","description":"Popis","date":"2025-04-19T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.4,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.2 \u2013 2025.1.3","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.4","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/05/10/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.1","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/04/14/post"}},"content":"### Popis\\n\\nTato aktualizace p\u0159in\xe1\u0161\xed nov\xe9 mo\u017enosti p\u0159izp\u016fsoben\xed joysticku, vylep\u0161en\xed u\u017eivatelsk\xe9ho rozhran\xed a d\u016fle\u017eit\xe9 opravy stability.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Zm\u011bny\\n\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba ve v\xfdb\u011bru kolekce blok\u016f v palet\u011b**: v\xfdb\u011br kolekce, posun na jinou a n\xe1vrat zp\u011bt nem\u011bl \u017e\xe1dn\xfd efekt.\\n- **Opraven p\xe1d aplikace p\u0159i na\u010d\xedt\xe1n\xed n\xe1ro\u010dn\xfdch profil\u016f** s velk\xfdm mno\u017estv\xedm blok\u016f.\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1na vlastnost \u201eTyp os\u201c** do nastaven\xed joysticku pro podporu **re\u017eimu s jednou osou** (X, Y, XY).\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1no barevn\xe9 odli\u0161en\xed** pro volantov\xe9 ovlada\u010de (\u201eGMZ\u201c, \u201eNo Mercy\u201c).\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1ny bloky \u201eje stisknuto\u201c** pro volanty a ped\xe1ly."},{"id":"/2025/04/14/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/04/14/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-04-14-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.1","description":"Popis","date":"2025-04-14T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.44,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.1","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.2 \u2013 2025.1.3","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/04/19/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"MOCPilot 2025.1.0","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/04/04/post"}},"content":"### Popis\\n\\nTato aktualizace obsahuje n\u011bkolik d\u016fle\u017eit\xfdch oprav chyb, kter\xe9 zlep\u0161uj\xed v\xfdkon, sni\u017euj\xed spot\u0159ebu baterie a zlep\u0161uj\xed chov\xe1n\xed blok\u016f v programovac\xedm prost\u0159ed\xed.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Zm\u011bny\\n\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba zp\u016fsobuj\xedc\xed vysok\xe9 vyu\u017eit\xed CPU, vyb\xedjen\xed baterie a n\xedzk\xfd v\xfdkon.**\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba, kdy bloky pro gamepad** (nap\u0159. \u201eje tla\u010d\xedtko stisknuto\u201c, \u201eje stisknuto tla\u010d\xedtko D-PAD\u201c) **nebylo mo\u017en\xe9 p\u0159ipojit k jin\xfdm blok\u016fm.**\\n- **Opraven probl\xe9m v bloku ud\xe1losti p\u0159ep\xedna\u010de krok\u016f**, kter\xfd nespr\xe1vn\u011b zpracov\xe1val dotykov\xe9 ud\xe1losti a po\u010d\xedt\xe1n\xed krok\u016f.\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba v bloku seznamu \u201epolo\u017eka ze\u201c**, kde nebylo mo\u017en\xe9 p\u0159ipojit v\xedce ne\u017e jeden blok jako index argumentu."},{"id":"/2025/04/04/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/04/04/post","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-04-04-post.md","title":"MOCPilot 2025.1.0","description":"\ud83d\ude80 Uzav\u0159en\xe1 beta verze MOCPilot 2025.1.0 pr\xe1v\u011b za\u010dala!","date":"2025-04-04T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.28,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"MOCPilot 2025.1.0","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025.1.1","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/cz/blog/2025/04/14/post"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 Uzav\u0159en\xe1 beta verze MOCPilot 2025.1.0 pr\xe1v\u011b za\u010dala!\\n\\nS radost\xed oznamujeme, \u017ee uzav\u0159en\xe9 beta testov\xe1n\xed MOCPilot 2025 je nyn\xed spu\u0161t\u011bno! Vybran\xed u\u017eivatel\xe9 mohou nyn\xed prozkoumat nov\xe9 funkce, poskytnout zp\u011btnou vazbu a pomoci formovat budoucnost aplikace MOCPilot.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\nPokud jste obdr\u017eeli pozv\xe1nku, zkontrolujte si sv\u016fj e-mail pro p\u0159\xedstupov\xe9 \xfadaje.  \\nD\u011bkujeme, \u017ee jste sou\u010d\xe1st\xed t\xe9to d\u016fle\u017eit\xe9 f\xe1ze!"}]}}')}}]);